name: lga_g09h_country_of_birth_by_age_by_sex_census_2016
title: LGA-G09h Country of Birth by Age by Sex-Census 2016

legal.licenceType: Creative Commons Attribution 2.5 Australia (CC BY 2.5 AU)

abstract:
LGA based data for Country of Birth of Person by Age by Sex, in General Community Profile (GCP), 2016 Census. Count of persons. G09 is broken up into 8 sections (G09a - G09h), this section contains 'Persons Papua New Guinea Age 0-4 years' - 'Persons Total Total'. The list of countries consists of the 50 most common Country of Birth responses reported in the 2011 Census. The data is by LGA 2016 boundaries. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
Note: There are small random adjustments made to all cell values to protect the confidentiality of data. These adjustments may cause the sum of rows or columns to differ by small amounts from table totals.
For more information visit the data source: http://www.abs.gov.au/census.
